just to get off the ground.

04:02.617 --> 04:04.953
Public opposition and red tape
can sometimes double that.

04:05.662 --> 04:08.539
But you can assume they've already
spent millions just getting this far.

04:08.915 --> 04:11.000
Wow. Now I really am glowing.

04:11.084 --> 04:12.710
Andrea Michele, the client.

04:12.794 --> 04:15.171
I'm told it's all about keeping
the customer happy here.

04:15.255 --> 04:17.548
-You are?
-This would be Alan Shore.

04:17.632 --> 04:20.009
Give me one week
and I'll get rid of that baby fat.

04:20.093 --> 04:22.178
I'm rather fond of my baby fat.

04:22.262 --> 04:25.265
-Great. Then you'll love mine.
-SHIRLEY: Uh, Andrea.

04:25.348 --> 04:27.141
Can we just get serious
about this case for a minute?

04:27.225 --> 04:28.351
ANDREA: Oh, I'm very serious.

04:28.434 --> 04:30.812
-Where shall we go to discuss it?
-How about my desk?

04:30.895 --> 04:35.024
Well, well, a little windmill tilting.
How fun. Don't get up.

04:35.108 --> 04:38.027
