But don't let the facts stop you.

08:40.436 --> 08:43.231
Let me call a witness, Judge. I can
tell you everything you need to know.

08:43.314 --> 08:46.108
-One o'clock.
-Wait! It's my motion!

08:46.192 --> 08:49.111
