Jerry, I'm deeply ashamed.

09:22.144 --> 09:25.982
-I don't understand.
-I feel hugely threatened by her.

09:26.065 --> 09:28.943
-I get this vibe.
-What vibe?

09:29.026 --> 09:30.111
That you like her.

09:30.194 --> 09:33.072
