11:16.258 --> 11:17.510
Come on, Alan.

11:17.593 --> 11:21.347
Once, before we go, let's swing.

11:22.556 --> 11:23.683
(nervous chuckle)

11:29.230 --> 11:30.064
LEIGH: Katie?

11:31.190 --> 11:34.068
