11:45.121 --> 11:48.416
Other than that, watch your back.

11:56.507 --> 11:58.759
A nuclear power plant
is actually very simple.

11:59.427 --> 12:03.097
We boil water to create steam
to turn a turbine to make electricity.

12:03.180 --> 12:07.059
But instead of burning fuel
to generate heat, we use nuclear fission.

12:07.143 --> 12:08.978
-What about greenhouse gases?
-None.

12:09.061 --> 12:10.146
-Acid rain?
-None.

12:10.229 --> 12:11.355
-Urban smog?
-None.

12:11.439 --> 12:13.023
