on Radiological Protection

12:37.298 --> 12:41.051
set the radiation exposure
limit at 100 rem per year.

12:41.135 --> 12:44.263
Anything under it was safe.
We now know they were wrong.

12:44.346 --> 12:46.974
-Yes.
-And in 1934,

12:47.057 --> 12:50.102
the National Council
on Radiation Protection

12:50.186 --> 12:52.521
set the standard at 36 rem per year.

12:52.855 --> 12:55.941
